query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM movie_keyword AS mk JOIN keyword AS k ON k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword = 'computer-animation' JOIN title AS t ON t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2010 JOIN complete_cast AS cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct1 ON cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast' JOIN comp_cast_type AS cct2 ON cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' JOIN movie_companies AS mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id JOIN company_name AS cn ON cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]' JOIN movie_info AS mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%') JOIN info_type AS it ON it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates' JOIN cast_info AS ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') JOIN role_type AS rt ON rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' JOIN name AS n ON n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name LIKE '%An%' JOIN char_name AS chn ON chn.id = ci.person_role_id JOIN person_info AS pi ON n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id JOIN info_type AS it3 ON it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND it3.info = 'trivia' JOIN aka_name AS an ON n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
